Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.06,0:00:09.93,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,我不知道為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.19,0:00:12.39,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.86,0:00:15.76,Default,Classmate B,0,0,0,,小和  你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:17.90,Default,Classmate A,0,0,0,,裕太  你搞什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.90,0:00:19.24,Default,Classmate A,0,0,0,,快向小和道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:23.42,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,我頭腦一熱  就會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.74,0:00:28.37,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,哪怕是雞毛蒜皮的小事  也會大打出手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.46,0:00:34.01,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,每當如此  老師都會找我媽媽談話
Comment: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:40.77,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,我這樣的性格  是個性  還是(疾病,BUG)呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:40.77,RUBY,Yuta,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(1299,980)}BUG
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:40.77,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,我這樣的性格  是個性  還是疾病呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.85,0:02:25.74,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,哦？ 開花了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.75,0:02:27.90,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,啊  須堂醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.90,0:02:29.71,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,要我買個自動澆水器嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:31.92,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,每天澆水很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:34.04,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,才不需要那種東西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:36.26,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,我澆的不是水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:38.50,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,我澆的是愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.50,0:02:40.33,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.33,0:02:42.01,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,你是在嘲笑我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.02,0:02:45.01,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,不  我覺得你說得很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.78,0:02:49.37,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,醫生誇獎我了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:51.52,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,那你也來一起澆…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:53.80,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,休息時間已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.97,0:02:56.54,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:03.75,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,怎麼樣？好吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:06.22,Default,Daughter,0,0,0,,嗯  超好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.44,0:03:10.07,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,孩子他爸  之後要去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:13.71,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,喂  孩子他爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.11,0:03:16.48,Default,Daughter,0,0,0,,爸爸  叫你呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:20.14,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,又發呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:21.77,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.77,0:03:24.07,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,你有什麼心事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.07,0:03:26.07,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,不  沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.07,0:03:29.73,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,我只是感慨  這樣的時間真是幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:32.02,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,像是謊言一般
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:37.23,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,好了  我們接下來去看電影…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.71,0:03:44.97,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:46.82,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.82,0:03:49.64,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,又做噩夢了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:52.56,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,抱歉  總是吵醒你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:55.28,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,講真  去醫院看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:58.55,Default,Daughter,0,0,0,,媽媽  尿尿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:02.64,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,嗯… 你說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.64,0:04:05.49,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,好  爸爸和你一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.49,0:04:07.37,Default,Daughter,0,0,0,,快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:16.57,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,在掃描您先生的電子腦的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:21.32,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,如果您知道可能導致他失眠的因素  請告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:24.89,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,他是個非常善良的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:27.46,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,但他過去好像遭受了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.46,0:04:31.34,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,可能有事情瞞著我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.34,0:04:33.33,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,為什麼這麼覺得？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:38.47,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,這事本來也不該告訴您的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:41.24,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,那這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:44.72,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,你為什麼每個月都向這個帳號轉錢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:47.46,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,而且還是這麼多錢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:51.43,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,你是不是被什麼人騙了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:53.10,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,讓我來幫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:54.85,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:57.89,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,以前有個叔叔給了我很多幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.37,0:05:02.36,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,我只是在給他工作的慈善機構捐款
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.08,0:05:05.86,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,這是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:10.00,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,我擔心他被捲入了什麼麻煩事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:13.87,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,記憶被篡改?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:18.49,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,嗯  那位患者的記憶在六年前受到篡改
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:23.94,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,很可能是由外部的強制介入改變的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.93,0:05:26.60,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,而且這種做法…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:31.81,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,並非是合法的正規治療法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:34.08,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,所以才是個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:37.47,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,但是松村完全沒有提到過…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.47,0:05:39.69,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,他可能忘記了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:41.48,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,要是調整他電子腦的醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:44.40,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,把他接受調整的記憶刪除了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:46.37,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,那也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.37,0:05:49.95,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,調整電子腦的手術  術後護理是必不可少的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.60,0:05:53.83,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,如果患者忘記了經歷手術這件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:05.33,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,這麼突然要出門  您是要去哪裡啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.33,0:06:07.39,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,我去見個老熟人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:11.72,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,開車要小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:13.69,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,一路順風
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:31.75,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,還特地到我這裡來拜訪…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:34.31,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,這是什麼風把你吹來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.21,0:06:37.07,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,這設備挺不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.07,0:06:38.66,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,看來你賺了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:40.29,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,也沒那麼誇張
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:41.83,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,先請坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:47.34,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,瀨戶  是你動了松島的電子腦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:50.60,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,你這又是來的哪一齣啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:52.42,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,我不知道你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.42,0:06:54.68,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,不過我可不能洩露病人的隱私…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:57.19,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,他應該還在給你轉錢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.49,0:07:00.33,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,不過他本人是說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:03.86,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,這是在給「叔叔」的慈善機構捐款
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:09.61,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,「叔叔」 我記得你寫過相關的論文吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:15.97,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,他因為持續多日的失眠和噩夢  前來我的診所就診
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.97,0:07:17.54,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,那些應該都是副作用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.94,0:07:21.63,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,我想知道你採取了什麼樣的治療
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:25.17,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,按你的風格  應該都有詳細記錄的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.33,0:07:29.42,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,我做的治療  你應該沒有猜錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.94,0:07:34.06,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,我在虛擬色情片上花了太多錢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:37.88,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,還因使用電子毒品惹上了警察
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.88,0:07:42.16,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,每次我都覺得自己完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.16,0:07:45.31,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,但是只要能戒掉酒精  我也能…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.78,0:07:49.66,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,的確  我能治好你的酒精成癮症
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.66,0:07:51.89,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,但是松島
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.89,0:07:55.95,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,你覺得你戒掉了酒癮就能幸福嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.77,0:08:02.28,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,如今你缺少改變自己的力量和意志
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:04.20,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,如果我就這樣治好了你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.20,0:08:07.07,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,你也會對別的東西成癮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.69,0:08:10.99,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,我… 到底是哪裡有問題？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:13.15,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,是我的腦袋嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:14.68,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,松島先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:16.02,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:20.79,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,你的腦袋和身體都沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:24.94,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,有問題的不是你  而是你的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:29.47,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,我的工作就是把它修回正軌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.37,0:08:34.97,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,我將他的電子腦固定成 SOL7 的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:37.45,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,然後和患者一起回顧過去的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.46,0:08:42.07,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,在關鍵點一處一處地施加誘導  「改良」過去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:43.60,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,對於松島來說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:45.91,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,只要能創造出他人生的「支柱」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.91,0:08:47.96,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,就自然能重振旗鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:52.34,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,你當真有取得他本人的許可吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:54.39,Default,Seto,0,1000,0,,那是自然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.39,0:08:58.35,Default,Seto,0,1000,0,,然後終於輪到那個「叔叔」登場了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:01.80,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,「叔叔」對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:04.40,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,「光是哭泣  什麼都改變不了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:08.77,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,該發火時就要發火」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:10.86,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,該發火時…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:13.01,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,對你施暴的父母
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.01,0:09:16.43,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,還有欺凌你的人  最終都向你道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:19.21,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,就因為你鼓起勇氣向他們發火了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:24.20,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,但是  我最後還是沒有去上學了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:28.38,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,那也是因為「叔叔」的建議
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.84,0:09:32.65,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,「叔叔」教會了你所有重要的人生道理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:37.16,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,你記得「叔叔」為你做了什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:40.39,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,我  不記得
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:43.81,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,讓我來幫你回想起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:48.73,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,他可是世界上最想讓你獲得幸福的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:54.98,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,你真就是只為了這件事而來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.98,0:09:57.53,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,千萬別忘記把數據發給我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:09:58.92,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.92,0:10:02.77,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,好啦  你就靠你的方法來抑制他的副作用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.77,0:10:03.88,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,啊對了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:07.16,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,這個  你拿一個回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:10.29,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,繁殖仙人掌可有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:12.79,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,我給你個袋子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:14.98,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,仙人掌是靠扦插來繁殖的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.98,0:10:18.39,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,生命力很強  所以照料起來也省事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.39,0:10:22.89,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,雖這麼說  但任何個體缺少了水都會枯死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:25.85,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,弱小的個體就只能放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:32.73,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,所以你就逆轉時間給他澆水了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:34.61,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,澆了充滿謊言的水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:37.86,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,那你會如何治療呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:40.69,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,光治好他的成癮症就算是大功告成？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.69,0:10:43.52,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,還是給他安排個精神護理機器人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:45.12,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,那樣可費時間囉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:50.21,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,哪怕是超 AI MICHI 也無法提高成年人的心理韌性哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:54.87,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,對這個患者來說  謊言是能夠根治他的特效藥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.87,0:10:57.50,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,你也多寬容一下謊言啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:11:01.00,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,能貫徹謊言的技術早就已經存在了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:03.47,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,莫加迪特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:06.47,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,作為同道中人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:09.02,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,你的事跡我也都有所耳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:13.73,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,你也不相信 MICHI 定下的規則是絕對正確
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:17.31,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,所以才會有個暗地裡的身份  不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:24.99,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,醫療沒有絕對的正確答案
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.73,0:11:30.75,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,在迎來了仿生人這一新成員的世界更是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:35.17,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,真讓人為難啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.25,0:11:40.80,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,真的是多謝你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:44.02,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,多虧了你們  我老公的失眠症也好轉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.02,0:11:45.77,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,我的睡眠不足也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:48.48,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.11,0:11:52.19,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,那個盆栽  我家也有一株
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.63,0:11:54.66,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,是有人送給醫生的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.09,0:11:58.99,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,我的好像也是別人送的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.99,0:12:00.84,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,是誰來著呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.84,0:12:03.59,Default,Daughter,0,0,0,,爸爸  還沒好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:05.96,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,嗯  已經搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.46,0:12:08.73,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,那我們先告辭了  醫生  多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.73,0:12:10.15,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.15,0:12:11.05,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.05,0:12:11.96,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:13.12,Default,Daughter,0,0,0,,走吧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:13.85,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,你想去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.85,0:12:14.82,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:19.14,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,你不告訴他記憶有被篡改過嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.14,0:12:20.52,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,告訴他了又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:23.48,Default,Daughter,0,0,0,,我想吃冰淇淋！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:24.47,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:27.97,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,說的… 也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.22,0:12:40.89,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,沒事的  不要怕  裕太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:42.99,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,媽媽會陪著你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:49.20,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,終於  我被帶到醫院去就診了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:10.51,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,欸  這是門德爾松嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.51,0:13:12.21,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.21,0:13:14.17,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,真是你彈的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:18.40,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,我也想聽聽你演奏的其他曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.40,0:13:21.02,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,方便的話  下次讓我聽聽看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:26.15,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,好了  診斷結束
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:31.14,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,我和你媽媽談話時  你去等待室稍等一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.03,0:13:38.54,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.55,0:13:42.05,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,可以讓診斷架構加入我們嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:43.92,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,他是醫療用 AI
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.93,0:13:46.42,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,好  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:48.94,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,傑  你能聽到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:50.68,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,我能聽到  須堂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.61,0:13:53.30,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,你有什麼看法？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.30,0:13:57.89,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,坦白說  我認為他可以被治療  也應該接受治療
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:00.57,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,如何治療？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:04.95,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,對情緒系統進行調律  是最簡單有效的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:08.45,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,對情緒系統… 調律？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:13.70,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,簡單來說就是要強行改變裕太的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.81,0:14:17.21,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,你這種說法太粗暴了  須堂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:18.87,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:20.97,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,讓我來解釋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:23.84,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,以人類為例
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:26.77,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,人類會因中樞神經的功能障礙等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.77,0:14:30.43,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,各種原因而產生社交障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:35.06,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,如果施以藥物療法或者改善習慣的心理療法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.06,0:14:37.85,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,基本上都要花費很長時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:39.74,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,但是換成是仿生人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.74,0:14:42.85,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,就可以直接微調其情緒機制
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.85,0:14:47.56,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,比給人類的藥物治療更加安全  也更有效
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.56,0:14:49.95,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,您有什麼疑問嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.67,0:14:55.33,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,有問題可以提出來  我為您解答
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:15:01.33,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,他真的需要… 這種治療嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:09.27,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,裕太無法控制住自己的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.27,0:15:12.23,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,但這可能就是他的個性
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:15.35,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,要是這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.89,0:15:21.61,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,這是尋求情緒系統調律的家屬中常見的顧慮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:23.67,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,不過  就數據而言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.67,0:15:26.23,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,術後對結果不滿的例子幾乎沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.23,0:15:27.09,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,基於這個情況…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.09,0:15:28.62,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,不用說了  傑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.62,0:15:29.84,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:36.88,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,沒有東西落在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:37.82,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.82,0:15:40.42,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,那下週再見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:42.23,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,等到那時再回復就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.23,0:15:43.11,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.11,0:15:45.20,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,那我們就先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:46.34,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,喂  少年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:49.76,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,下次來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:52.90,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,當真要帶其他曲子的錄音來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:54.73,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,我之前說的可不是客套話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:15:59.06,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,真的是太對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:01.24,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,沒關係  不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.24,0:16:03.73,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,等… 等一下  裕太
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.18,0:16:09.89,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,她會同意接受治療嗎  他母親
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.89,0:16:12.85,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,大概會吧  很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.46,0:16:14.49,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,遺憾？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.18,0:16:20.99,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,我喜歡鋼琴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.17,0:16:24.23,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,鋼琴不會和我吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:27.14,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,鋼琴不會背叛我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:29.50,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,我敲下「哆」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:31.18,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,它一定會以「哆」回應我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.18,0:16:34.58,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,把各種聲音排列起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:36.56,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,在演奏時感覺真是棒極了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:39.60,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,僅僅由我和…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:40.73,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,鋼琴組成的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:43.00,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,裕太  裕太
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.53,0:16:48.59,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,裕太  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.59,0:16:49.77,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,該吃晚餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.78,0:16:52.88,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,但是  我剛剛在錄音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.88,0:16:55.16,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,正在狀態呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.63,0:16:59.09,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,媽媽不也常常跟你說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.09,0:17:00.97,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,你必須得改變自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:01.87,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:03.20,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.20,0:17:05.74,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,為什麼媽媽會這樣?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.74,0:17:08.33,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,為什麼?! 為什麼?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.35,0:17:12.21,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,感覺腦子裡被填滿了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.14,0:17:15.31,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,全是痛苦的情緒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.31,0:17:16.82,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,非常難受
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:22.73,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,我只要有鋼琴就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:26.30,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,但是… 其他人會來礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:27.48,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,如果他們能消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:31.12,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,如果他們都能消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.12,0:17:32.70,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,一定就能爽快多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.74,0:17:37.82,Default,Classmate A,0,0,0,,你在瞪什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:39.20,Default,Classmate A,0,0,0,,有錯的人是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.21,0:17:41.73,Default,Classmate B,0,0,0,,我們對你做什麼了嗎  裕太？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.73,0:17:43.37,Default,Classmate B,0,0,0,,什麼都沒做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:45.71,Default,Classmate C,0,0,0,,向小和道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.22,0:17:54.86,Default,Nodoka,0,0,0,,當時我只是問你在聽什麼曲子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.91,0:17:59.09,Default,Nodoka,0,0,0,,你總是一個人  所以我想交個朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.92,0:18:06.45,Default,Nodoka,0,0,0,,結果你突然把我推開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:07.69,Default,Classmate B,0,0,0,,快道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:08.80,Default,Classmate C,0,0,0,,道歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:09.73,Default,Classmate A,0,0,0,,道歉  裕太！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:15.62,Default,Classmate B,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:16.78,Default,Classmate C,0,0,0,,搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.50,0:18:41.05,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,為什麼我當時會那麼固執呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.94,0:18:44.18,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,事到如今  我也不搞清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.84,0:18:45.85,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:52.01,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,因為在那之後  我接受了治療
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.24,0:18:58.03,Default,Yuta's Mom,0,0,0,,我的兒子也能交到很多朋友嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.62,0:19:01.52,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,嗯  應該是可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.52,0:19:05.29,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,要知道一直以來  就只有鋼琴是他朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:16.82,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,你感覺怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.61,0:19:21.30,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,有什麼地方不舒服嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:27.61,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,我感覺  沒問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.59,0:19:32.02,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,還有  我帶來了演奏的錄音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:37.37,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,真厲害  全是我喜歡的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:39.32,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,我可以收下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.33,0:19:40.32,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:44.32,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,因為叔叔你誇獎了我的演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:49.60,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,是嗎  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:54.85,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,從那天以來…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:58.44,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,我就變得可以非常冷靜地看待自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.18,0:20:04.62,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,也很少有熱血上頭的情況了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.32,0:20:12.88,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,也能和班上的同學交好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.11,0:20:32.12,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,裕太  飯做好了  快來吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:41.51,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,我現在依舊喜歡鋼琴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.00,0:20:49.37,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,但… 我感覺我彈奏的音色和過去有所不同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:07.78,Default,Rika,0,0,0,,這鋼琴彈得真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.24,0:21:09.65,Default,Rika,0,0,0,,這是什麼曲子？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.65,0:21:11.71,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,帕蒂塔第一組曲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.71,0:21:13.05,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,彈得不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:15.22,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.22,0:21:17.72,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,每個音符都感覺繃得很緊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.72,0:21:20.55,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,但讓人感覺非常美妙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.19,0:21:25.67,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,這是之前那個男孩演奏的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.52,0:21:29.08,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,不過這是他在接受治療前的演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.81,0:21:35.06,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:40.07,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,要改變仿生人的性格…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:42.65,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,在技術上並不困難
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.24,0:21:49.07,Default,Female Patient,0,0,0,,我的人生為什麼會變成這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.07,0:21:52.49,Default,Seto,0,0,0,flashback,我的工作就是把它修回正軌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.61,0:21:57.12,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,創造虛假的記憶也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.43,0:22:00.18,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:04.63,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,須堂  方便說兩句嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.63,0:22:05.64,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.64,0:22:07.70,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,關於裕太的治療
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.70,0:22:11.21,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,你是否滿意我的診斷？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.32,0:22:14.63,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,你的工作總是完成得很出色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.91,0:22:17.65,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,不用擔心  沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.64,0:22:20.01,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,非常感謝
